text: Walking Tall is an American action movie with "The Rock", also known as Dwayne Johnson, starring in it. It is set in Kitsap County, Washington. The main character carries a 2x4 piece of wood and uses it as a weapon against the bad guys. == Other websites == * Category:2004 movies Category:American action movies Category:Movies set in Washington (state) Category:English-language movies
title: Walking Tall
